&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Retirement:&lt;/strong&gt; 401(k) plan with generous company match and annual profit-sharing contribution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Time Off:&lt;/strong&gt; Open PTO policy and 11 paid company holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No-Touch Freight:&lt;/strong&gt; 100% no loading or unloading of trailers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
