&lt;li&gt;Build low latency/high throughput, fault tolerant &amp;nbsp;batch or stream processing systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build scalable backend services for data search and data curation systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write high quality Python and SQL.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
